This paper deals with conjunctive query answering over ontologies, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses acyclicity notions, which are related to logic (cs.LO) and complexity theory (cs.CR). Finally, the paper proposes a more efficient reasoning procedure, which could be of interest to computer architecture (cs.CC) researchers.
